HEADWORD: Jaundiced
<hw>Jaun"diced</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Affected with jaundice.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Jaundiced</qex> eyes seem to see all objects yellow.</q>
